# Data

The analyses in this repository are based on publicly available datasets.

## Human single-cell RNA-seq

AMP Lupus Nephritis Consortium (ImmPort SDY997)

Processed Seurat objects are not included in this repository because of file size limitations.

To reproduce the analysis:

1. Download SDY997 from ImmPort.
2. Download the CEL-seq expression matrix and metadata.
3. Build the Seurat object following Script 01.
